@FunctionalInterface public interface PostControlsCallbackQueryCommand extends CallbackQueryCommand<MessageIdsCommandCallbackDataDTO>
A command interface for handling callback queries related to post controls. This interface extends the generic CallbackQueryCommand with a specific type of callback data, MessageIdsCommandCallbackDataDTO.
